'''Peter Hambleton''' is a New Zealand actor who portrayed [[Glóin]], one of the thirteen [[Hobbits]] in [[Thorin and Company|Thorin and his Company]], in [[The Hobbit (film series)|''The Hobbit'' (film series)]]. He also performed the motion capture and voice work of [[William]] the [[Troll]] in [[The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey]].<ref>[[Peter Jackson]], "Production begins in New Zealand on The Hobbit" dated 20 March 2011, Facebook(accessed 22 December 2011)</ref>

